snippet.title: Vox Machinae - Trailer (2018)
snippet.description:
A new trailer for the upcoming VR-supporting giant robot combat action simulation, Vox Machinae!
Interested in helping test Vox Machinae and providing helpful feedback? Follow this link:
http://voxmachinae.com/playtest.shtml
